  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Get ready for an exciting adventure in the epic tank battles.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/19eb4e006c46c9d4c5c99568d0e10f2b.poster.avif?t=1750045587\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/19eb4e006c46c9d4c5c99568d0e10f2b.webm?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/19eb4e006c46c9d4c5c99568d0e10f2b.mp4?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into your tank and plunge into the  fierce tank battles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to fight on modern technology. Pumping begins with combat vehicles of the mid-20th century, and the latest tanks become available at the last levels! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/25043175333e39ece687f9f421c1382a.poster.avif?t=1750045587\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/25043175333e39ece687f9f421c1382a.webm?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/25043175333e39ece687f9f421c1382a.mp4?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Improve your tank to become stronger than your rivals!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Invite your friends and play with them ABSOLUTELY FOR FREE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/414520625b4060bf7e51d304a02e25ea.poster.avif?t=1750045587\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/414520625b4060bf7e51d304a02e25ea.webm?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/414520625b4060bf7e51d304a02e25ea.mp4?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>specifications :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Dynamic tank battles, solid action with no time for respite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Many systems for the development and pumping of your tank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Lots of camouflage and drawings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Multiple battle arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Intuitive operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Daily combat quests, for which you can get bonuses to strengthen your tank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The ability to choose any game mode: team or individual.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• A general chat that allows you to communicate with the players of your country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Join our fan communities:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/980c5ea8aa6e7cd9b2139100223631b2.poster.avif?t=1750045587\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/980c5ea8aa6e7cd9b2139100223631b2.webm?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/980c5ea8aa6e7cd9b2139100223631b2.mp4?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be aware of the newest updates!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take part in gaming tournaments, take first place in the ranking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Fill your life with thrills, start your battle!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into your tank and prove to everyone who you are! Until you accept the fight, you won't know...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tanks, tanks and more tanks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PERMANENT INTERNET CONNECTION IS REQUIRED.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Get ready for an exciting adventure in the epic tank battles.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/19eb4e006c46c9d4c5c99568d0e10f2b.poster.avif?t=1750045587\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/19eb4e006c46c9d4c5c99568d0e10f2b.webm?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/19eb4e006c46c9d4c5c99568d0e10f2b.mp4?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into your tank and plunge into the  fierce tank battles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to fight on modern technology. Pumping begins with combat vehicles of the mid-20th century, and the latest tanks become available at the last levels! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/25043175333e39ece687f9f421c1382a.poster.avif?t=1750045587\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/25043175333e39ece687f9f421c1382a.webm?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/25043175333e39ece687f9f421c1382a.mp4?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Improve your tank to become stronger than your rivals!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Invite your friends and play with them ABSOLUTELY FOR FREE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/414520625b4060bf7e51d304a02e25ea.poster.avif?t=1750045587\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/414520625b4060bf7e51d304a02e25ea.webm?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/414520625b4060bf7e51d304a02e25ea.mp4?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>specifications :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Dynamic tank battles, solid action with no time for respite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Many systems for the development and pumping of your tank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Lots of camouflage and drawings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Multiple battle arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Intuitive operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Daily combat quests, for which you can get bonuses to strengthen your tank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The ability to choose any game mode: team or individual.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• A general chat that allows you to communicate with the players of your country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Join our fan communities:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/980c5ea8aa6e7cd9b2139100223631b2.poster.avif?t=1750045587\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/980c5ea8aa6e7cd9b2139100223631b2.webm?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/782660/extras/980c5ea8aa6e7cd9b2139100223631b2.mp4?t=1750045587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be aware of the newest updates!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take part in gaming tournaments, take first place in the ranking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Fill your life with thrills, start your battle!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into your tank and prove to everyone who you are! Until you accept the fight, you won't know...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tanks, tanks and more tanks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A PERMANENT INTERNET CONNECTION IS REQUIRED.</p>",
